      "updated": 1777109921532,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional requirements\n- User retrieves short url for provided long url\n- Optional custom alias (hash)\n- Optional expiration date\n\n- Redirect when accessing the shortened url\n\nNon functional requirements\n- Short urls are unique\n- Low latency redirects <100ms\n- Availability 99.99%\n- 1B Urls\n- 100M DAU\n\nRead to write ratio up to 1000:1\n\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": "DmbJG3t-s488I13QzJSsb",
      "originalText": "Functional requirements\n- User retrieves short url for provided long url\n- Optional custom alias (hash)\n- Optional expiration date\n\n- Redirect when accessing the shortened url\n\nNon functional requirements\n- Short urls are unique\n- Low latency redirects <100ms\n- Availability 99.99%\n- 1B Urls\n- 100M DAU\n\nRead to write ratio up to 1000:1\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
